<p>
  <span class="nym">Alexis</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Ancient Greek</span> <i>Ἄλεξις</i> or <i>Ἀλέξιος</i> 'defender'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 4th-5th C Roman saint, a 10th-11th C Byzantine emperor, a 12th C Byzantine emperor, a 12th-13th C Byzantine emperor, two 13th C Byzantine emperors, a 13th C emperor of Trebizond, two 14th C emperors of Trebizond, a 14th C Russian saint, and a 15th C emperor of Trebizond.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


